featured_reviews.review_id: I don't normally leave reviews but my experience here a few days ago has me wanting to make sure this employee gets recognized. From the moment I walked into the store Levy made me feel completely at ease. This was my first time going into an actual adult store, haven't had the courage to do it. She welcomed me with a smile and offered her assistance should I need it. I was a little overwhelmed at the amount of different toys and ended up pacing for a few minutes trying to figure out what the heck I was looking for. She came over and asked if I needed help. I explained it was my first time and I had no idea what I was looking for. She was very kind and understanding, which she had no idea how much that meant to me. What could have been a terrible, embarrassing experience was actually an easy fun one. By the end of it we were laughing like old friends. I don't know if the owners read these reviews but I hope you read this one. Levy is an amazing employee and I can't tell you how lucky you are to have her. I will definitely be a repeat customer as long as she is there! Already planning my next visit as her recommendation was spot on and now I want more haha. If I could give 10 stars for customer experience I would. Don't miss out on this place and ask for Levy when you go! You won't be disappointed!!

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Normalde degerlendirme birakmam ama birkac gun once burada yasadigim deneyim, bu calisanin tanindigindan emin olmak istememi sagladi. Magazaya girdigim andan itibaren Levy beni tamamen rahatlatti. Bu benim gercek bir yetiskin magazasina ilk gidisimdi, buna cesaret edemedim. Beni bir gulumsemeyle karsiladi ve ihtiyacim olursa yardim etmeyi teklif etti. Farkli oyuncaklarin miktari beni biraz bunaltti ve sonunda ne aradigimi anlamaya calisarak birkac dakika volta attim. Yanima geldi ve yardima ihtiyacim olup olmadigini sordu. Bunun ilk seferim oldugunu ve ne aradigim hakkinda hicbir fikrim olmadigini acikladim. Cok nazik ve anlayisliydi ve bunun benim icin ne kadar onemli oldugu hakkinda hicbir fikri yoktu. Korkunc, utanc verici bir deneyim olabilecek sey aslinda kolay ve eglenceli bir deneyimdi. Sonunda eski arkadaslar gibi guluyorduk. Sahiplerin bu yorumlari okuyup okumadigini bilmiyorum ama umarim bunu okursunuz. Levy harika bir calisan ve ona sahip oldugunuz icin ne kadar sansli oldugunuzu anlatamam. Orada oldugu surece kesinlikle tekrar musteri olacagim! Onun tavsiyesi yerinde oldugu icin zaten bir sonraki ziyaretimi planliyorum ve simdi daha fazlasini istiyorum haha. Musteri deneyimine 10 yildiz verebilseydim verirdim. Burayi kacirmayin ve gittiginizde Levy'yi isteyin! Hayal kirikligina ugramayacaksiniz!

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Tamam yer. Bir suru golgeli karakterle cok kirli. Oncelikle uyusturucu saticilari ve haydutlar burayi yonetiyor gibi gorunuyor. Orada bir arkadasla tanistim, otoparkta dolasan, anlatan ve bagiran insanlar vardi. Bir sure oturduktan sonra bir adam pencereye dokunuyor ve 30 dakika icinde acilacagini soyluyor. Disarida calisan insanlarin bakislari simdiden rahatsiz ediciydi. Adam iceri girdikten sonra, agzi altin dislerle dolu bir kolsuz bluz ve parmak arasi terliklerle 170 civarinda tek kelime etmeden kapida durmus bakiyordu. Onun icin durmaya basladim ama sonra yardimci olmayacagini anladim, onu gectik. Magaza guzel ve temizdi. "Konsept" bile iyiydi. Ama yer kirli. Gercekten kirli demek istiyorum. Lekelerle dolu beyaz deri bir koltuk vardi. Film buyuk ekranda sessizdi. Personel gereksiz yere gelmeye devam etti. Bir noktada bir kadin geldi ve sesi duzeltmesi gerektigini iddia ederek bir masanin uzerine cikti. Golgeli kirli yer. Sadece kalabaliga geri donecekti.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Ne yaparsaniz yapin, ne ucret aldiklarina dair bir web sitesine inanmayin! Kapida ikiye katlanir. Bunu sordugunuzda personel kaba ve umursamiyor. Ciftlere karsi pek arkadasca davranmadilar. Ciftlere iyi davranilirsa erkeklerin takip edecegini ve dolayisiyla daha fazla gelir elde edecegini dusunursunuz, DURUM DEGIL, umurlarinda degil. Her gittigimizde ciftler icin 10 dolar diyorlar, oraya vardigimizda ise 20 dolar oluyor.

8-29'da tekrar denedim, asagi inmeden once bir kez daha aradim ve cift basina 20 dolar ve bedava icki dediler. Oraya vardik ve 40 dolar dedi ve bedava icecek yoktu! Bu adamlar dolandirici. Onlarla tartistim ve gidecegimizi soyledim, o da parayi 20 dolara dusurdu. Orada sadece 2590b uzeri kizlar vardi ve bekar erkekler yoktu. Muzigin sesi o kadar yuksekti ki rahatsiz ediciydi. Bu adamlarin bir kulubu nasil yoneteceklerine dair hicbir fikri yok, uzak durun.

featured_reviews.review_id:
I get what
reviewer "Dream Car" is saying... we never did go there as when we called it turned out to be someone's cell phone rather then the number of the business. The prices they quoted were much higher than what we saw listed on their ad on the web somewhere (which is where we found out about it). A few months later we thought they'd be more established as before they had recently opened and this time the prices quoted were higher yet.

From our experience so far we're wondering how these guys stay in business with alternatives such as the Lido and New Fine Arts as well as free postings on CL.

Update aug 2021.. I don't want to seem unfairly harsh so even though we haven't found time to visit  them yet I feel I should point out that the cell phone  misadventure  was probably just typical "start up" pains and also that with wireless  has come opportunities for  ownership to manage their enterprises in a more hand's on way. I haven't had  an update as to if they are still  taking such a direct approach in day to day operations but I have a feeling they are .. and actually it would be welcomed by most patrons of any business using modern tools in such a progressive way so I think that my earlier comments were perhaps unenlightened as I failed to consider the advantages of the approach.
I'll leave the original comments alone , at least for now... It shows how my thinking has evolved. Sort of calling myself out for not seeing that before.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
ne anladim
"Dream Car" yorumcusu diyor ki... biz oraya hic gitmedik cunku aradigimizda bunun isyerinin numarasi degil de birinin cep telefonu oldugu ortaya cikti. Teklif ettikleri fiyatlar, internette bir yerlerdeki reklamlarinda listeledigimiz fiyatlardan cok daha yuksekti (bunu oradan ogrendik). Birkac ay sonra, yakin zamanda acilmadan onceki gibi daha koklu olacaklarini ve bu sefer teklif edilen fiyatlarin daha yuksek olacagini dusunduk.

Su ana kadarki deneyimlerimize dayanarak, bu adamlarin Lido ve Yeni Guzel Sanatlar gibi alternatiflerin yani sira CL'deki ucretsiz ilanlarla is hayatinda nasil kaldiklarini merak ediyoruz.

Agustos 2021 guncellemesi.. Haksizca sert gorunmek istemiyorum, bu yuzden henuz onlari ziyaret etmek icin zaman bulamamis olsak da, cep telefonu talihsizliginin muhtemelen sadece tipik "baslangic" sancilari oldugunu belirtmem gerektigini dusunuyorum. Kablosuz teknolojiyle birlikte isletmelerini daha kolay yonetebilmeleri icin sahip olma firsatlari da ortaya cikti. Gunluk operasyonlarda hala bu kadar dogrudan bir yaklasim benimseyip izlemedikleri konusunda bir guncelleme almadim, ancak oyle olduklarini hissediyorum.. ve aslinda boyle bir durumda modern araclari kullanan herhangi bir isletmenin cogu patronu tarafindan memnuniyetle karsilanacaktir. Bu yuzden yaklasimin avantajlarini goz onunde bulunduramadigim icin daha onceki yorumlarimin belki de aydinlatilmamis oldugunu dusunuyorum.
Orijinal yorumlari bir kenara birakacagim, en azindan simdilik... Bu benim dusuncemin nasil gelistigini gosteriyor. Bunu daha once gormedigim icin kendime sesleniyor gibiyim.

I recently had the pleasure of shopping at Alternatives and I must say, the customer service Devin provided was nothing short of exceptional. featured_reviews.review_id:
I've been visiting Alternatives for a few years now and I must say, I've noticed some changes in workplace dynamics over the years. Specifically, there was one morning I stopped in and there was an altercation between Mike and one of the other employees (Devon I think his name was). I don 't know the details of the argument, but i do know Mike was screaming and yelling at Devon in a very degrading manner in front of me and other customers inside the facility. So much it came for me to write this review because I did not find his angry yelling at him 1). appropriate for the workplace and 2). appropriate for a superior to be reprimanding an employee like this in front of customers and other employees. What struck as interesting to me is how he treated the morning shift employee and how he treated the night shift employee - completely different in tone, attitude and mannerism. Seems like Mike is initiating a tense environment in the store. As a man who's worked in corporate insurance sales, I've witnessed and been at the forefront of toxic work environments and from my experience, this is what it seems to look like at Alternatives with Mike, which I can't find to appreciate.
I love the products, really enjoy the theater and absolutely love how clean and organized the store is. However, I don't love the sense of toxicity I get from being there.

featured_reviews.review_id: My boyfriend and I went into this location last night looking for a particular item. It is right around the corner from where I live and I have never shopped at Adam & Eve before, so I decided I wanted to try it out, rather than going a little further to New Fine Arts, where I typically shop. We were approached 5 times during our approximately 30 minute shopping experience. Once when we came in, which was nice. A different person approached us once. A third person approached us 3 different times after I picked up a couple of things. Assistance is great, but this was clearly not a service oriented visit. This employee asked me 3 times if I wanted her to take my items to the front to hold. This in and of itself may not have been such a big deal, except for a few other factors at play. I was holding them because I was trying to choose, and touching something that was going to be applied to my skin in an intimate way was very much a part of the process to decide which item we would pay $30-$50 for that could not (obviously) be returned, if I didn't like it. Also, we were having intimate conversation and debating our choice. Usually we have a lot of fun together when looking for new things. This was not a fun experience. featured_reviews.review_id:
Me and my wife, newlyweds on our honeymoon,  just left this place.  We have to say it was our first experience at anyplace like this and we had no idea what to expect.
We were met at the door by the bouncer.  A big intimidating guy that within a few minutes actually had us laughing and comfortable.  (If you go there tell "Big Purp" you read this review.  He will know who posted it.)
The young lady working the register explained that it was couples night and also reassured us and made us comfortable.
After showing us the couples area, which was really nice and relaxing, we decided to try it.  We stayed 4-5 hours and never felt perved on or uncomfortable.   All the other couples were super cool and polite and while we were watched, we never felt threatened or uneasy.
Big Purp made his rounds, visited just enough to be polite, and we didn't see any single men which was nice.  Don't get me wrong, there was quite a few there but not in the area for couples night.
We can't say enough good things about the staff and how grateful we were to have chosen to go here.

featured_reviews.review_id:
My girlfriend and I passed by the Sara's Secret in Fort Worth during a road trip from KS to Austin, Texas, and stopped in on a whim. We proceeded to ruin our travel itinerary for the day by spending almost two hours there. So when we passed by this one in Dallas, we were excited to have another adventure. We were left sorely disappointed.

The location in Fort Worth was clean, well-lit, spacious, and unintimidating, with a HUGE selection. Display models of products and test models abounded. The employees were friendly and knowledgeable, polite, friendly and well-dressed. NONE of these things were true of this location in Dallas.

The store is cramped and crowded compared to the Forth Worth location, with not nearly as good a selection. Fully 30-40% of the inventory was cheap novelty "bridal shower" gag gift stuff and cheaply-made polyester lingerie, not actual lovemaking aides and products. It felt very sleezy and creepy, which is exactly what you're trying to *avoid* when you go to a sex shoppe. The speakers were blasting awful, static-filled radio that was 75% ads for "winnable" concert tickets and payday loans and such. Most of the higher-end products on display were behind glass, as opposed to the Fort Worth location where everything was easy to access and handle to make an informed purchase.

The one employee on staff was rude and stand-offish, and didn't offer to help even when my girlfriend and I were visibly confused and torn between two different products. Despite the store being small enough that she could keep constant tabs on us from behind the counter, she spent the whole time we were there pretending to dust the shelves 3 feet away from us. I assume she thought we were going to shoplift and was wanting to catch us at it. I feel weird mentioning this, but she was also dressed very sloppily and clearly hadn't taken any care with her appearance. Don't get me wrong, I'm not some sort of chauvinist who thinks sex shoppes should only be filled with beautiful young female employees - but with the stigma associated with sex shoppes, you at least want the employees (male or female) to comport themselves in a way that makes the establishment feel upscale and classy, rather than sleezy and sloppy. This employee's appearance and demeanor made me feel like she was trying to sell me illicit drugs, not body-positive sex toys.

In short, this store is small, poorly-stocked, poorly-run, and the employees make you feel judged for wanting to buy the products they're ostensibly trying to sell you. Spend the extra time to go to the Fort Worth location. You'll be glad you did.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Kiz arkadasim ve ben KS'den Austin, Teksas'a yaptigimiz bir yolculuk sirasinda Fort Worth'taki Sara'nin Sirri'ndan gectik ve bir hevesle ugradik. Orada neredeyse iki saat gecirerek gunluk seyahat programimizi mahvetmeye basladik. Dallas'ta bunun yanindan gectigimizde baska bir maceraya atilmanin heyecanini yasadik. Buyuk bir hayal kirikligi yasadik.

Fort Worth'taki konum temiz, iyi aydinlatilmis, ferah ve goz korkutmayan, BUYUK bir secimdi. Urunlerin teshir modelleri ve test modelleri cok fazlaydi. Calisanlar guleryuzlu ve bilgili, kibar, arkadas canlisi ve iyi giyimliydi. Bunlarin HICBIRI Dallas'taki bu konum icin dogru degildi.

Magaza, Forth Worth lokasyonuna kiyasla sikisik ve kalabalik, pek iyi bir secim yok. Envanterin tamamen %30-40'i, gercek sevisme yardimcilari ve urunleri degil, ucuz yenilik "gelin partisi" saka hediyeleri ve ucuza yapilmis polyester ic camasirlarindan olusuyordu. Cok uykulu ve urkutucu hissettiriyordu ki, seks shop'a gittiginizde *kacinmaya* calistiginiz sey de tam olarak bu. Hoparlorler, %75'i "kazanilabilir" konser biletleri, avans kredileri ve benzeri reklamlardan olusan berbat, statik dolu radyoyu patlatiyorlardi. Bilgili bir satin alma islemi gerceklestirmek icin her seye erisimin ve kullanimin kolay oldugu Fort Worth lokasyonunun aksine, sergilenen ust duzey urunlerin cogu camin arkasindaydi.

Personelden tek calisan kaba ve mesafeli davrandi ve kiz arkadasimla benim kafamizin gozle gorulur bir sekilde karistigi ve iki farkli urun arasinda kaldigimizda bile yardim teklifinde bulunmadi. Magaza tezgahin arkasindan bizi surekli takip edebilecek kadar kucuk olmasina ragmen, orada oldugumuz sure boyunca bizden 3 metre uzaktaki raflarin tozunu aliyormus gibi yaparak gecirdi. Sanirim hirsizlik yapacagimizi dusundu ve bizi yakalamak istedi. Bunu soylerken kendimi tuhaf hissediyorum ama ayni zamanda cok ozensiz giyinmisti ve gorunusune hic dikkat etmedigi belliydi. Beni yanlis anlamayin, seks shop'larin sadece guzel genc kadin calisanlarla doldurulmasi gerektigini dusunen bir cesit sovenist degilim - ama seks shop'larla ilgili damgalama nedeniyle, en azindan calisanlarin (erkek veya kadin) sunu yapmasini istiyorsunuz: Kendilerini, kurumun uyusuk ve ozensiz olmaktan ziyade, luks ve sik hissettirecek sekilde hareket etmelerini saglayin. Bu calisanin gorunusu ve tavri bana vucut pozitif seks oyuncaklari degil, yasa disi uyusturucu satmaya calisiyormus gibi hissettirdi.

Kisacasi, bu magaza kucuk, stoklari az, kotu isletilen bir magaza ve calisanlar, gorunuste size satmaya calistiklari urunleri satin almak istedikleri icin sizi yargilanmis hissettiriyorlar. Ekstra zamani Fort Worth lokasyonuna gitmek icin harcayin. Bunu yaptigina memnun olacaksin.

featured_reviews.review_id: I firmly believe in supporting small business but I will never shop here again. I've spent hundreds of dollars shopping here and I've never once been offered help without asking first. Today I came with my girl to reup on a lube that we enjoy and a half hairline employee walked up and asked her to put her purse behind the counter. In a normal store this wouldn't bother me much. But dude didn't introduce himself or offer help or anything. Just immediately said that she had to put her purse behind the counter. I don't know about y'all but I don't like being treated like a thief where I'm about to spend my hard earned money. Especially when everything that they sell is cheaper on Amazon. I just prefer to support brick and mortar stores. It's amazing that they can never approach me to offer products when I come in but they get extreme confidence when it comes to disrespecting me and questioning if I'm going to buy there. I'm an otr trucker and I'll gladly take that money elsewhere.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Kucuk isletmeleri desteklemeye kesinlikle inaniyorum ama bir daha asla buradan alisveris yapmayacagim. Burada alisveris yapmak icin yuzlerce dolar harcadim ve bana sormadan bir kez bile yardim teklif edilmedi. Bugun sevdigimiz bir madeni yag almak icin kizimla birlikte geldim ve yarim ince bir calisan geldi ve ondan cantasini tezgahin arkasina koymasini istedi. Normal bir magazada bu beni pek rahatsiz etmezdi. Ama ahbap kendini tanitmadi, yardim falan teklif etmedi. Hemen cantasini tezgahin arkasina koymasi gerektigini soyledi. Sizi bilmiyorum ama zor kazandigim parayi harcamak uzereyken hirsiz muamelesi gormekten hoslanmiyorum. Ozellikle sattiklari her sey Amazon'da daha ucuzken. Ben sadece gercek mekanda faaliyet gosteren magazalari desteklemeyi tercih ederim. Geldigimde urun teklif etmek icin bana asla yaklasamamalari, ancak is bana saygisizlik etmek ve oradan satin alip almayacagimi sorgulamak oldugunda asiri guven duymalari sasirtici. Ben bir otr kamyon soforuyum ve o parayi baska bir yerden seve seve alirim.

featured_reviews.review_id: Went inside the store with my baby (barely a year and a half), they told me to leave. If they smoked inside, I would have totally been on board with leaving, but they didn't. I rejoined my husband in another store over. He asked me if I wanted to leave her with him and go back, I said no. When we went back to our car, we watched a couple with a stroller go inside, and not be kicked out like I was. Be consistent. That's why this review is being written.
